            "api_nlt_to_ref": "2Kgs.6:1-7:20",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E2%20Kings%206%3A1-7%3A20%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_1%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E2%20Kings%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Floating%20Ax%20Head%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20day%20the%20group%20of%20prophets%20came%20to%20Elisha%20and%20told%20him%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BAs%20you%20can%20see%2C%20this%20place%20where%20we%20meet%20with%20you%20is%20too%20small.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_2%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3ELet%26%23x2019%3Bs%20go%20down%20to%20the%20Jordan%20River%2C%20where%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20logs.%20There%20we%20can%20build%20a%20new%20place%20for%20us%20to%20meet.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BAll%20right%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20told%20them%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Bgo%20ahead.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_3%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BPlease%20come%20with%20us%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20someone%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20will%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20said.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_4%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20he%20went%20with%20them.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EWhen%20they%20arrived%20at%20the%20Jordan%2C%20they%20began%20cutting%20down%20trees.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_5%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20as%20one%20of%20them%20was%20cutting%20a%20tree%2C%20his%20ax%20head%20fell%20into%20the%20river.%20%26%23x201C%3BOh%2C%20sir!%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20cried.%20%26%23x201C%3BIt%20was%20a%20borrowed%20ax!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_6%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhere%20did%20it%20fall%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20man%20of%20God%20asked.%20When%20he%20showed%20him%20the%20place%2C%20Elisha%20cut%20a%20stick%20and%20threw%20it%20into%20the%20water%20at%20that%20spot.%20Then%20the%20ax%20head%20floated%20to%20the%20surface.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_7%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGrab%20it%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20Elisha%20said.%20And%20the%20man%20reached%20out%20and%20grabbed%20it.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_8%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EElisha%20Traps%20the%20Arameans%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20the%20king%20of%20Aram%20was%20at%20war%20with%20Israel%2C%20he%20would%20confer%20with%20his%20officers%20and%20say%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWe%20will%20mobilize%20our%20forces%20at%20such%20and%20such%20a%20place.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_9%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20immediately%20Elisha%2C%20the%20man%20of%20God%2C%20would%20warn%20the%20king%20of%20Israel%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BDo%20not%20go%20near%20that%20place%2C%20for%20the%20Arameans%20are%20planning%20to%20mobilize%20their%20troops%20there.%26%23x201D%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_10%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20king%20of%20Israel%20would%20send%20word%20to%20the%20place%20indicated%20by%20the%20man%20of%20God.%20Time%20and%20again%20Elisha%20warned%20the%20king%2C%20so%20that%20he%20would%20be%20on%20the%20alert%20there.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_11%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%20of%20Aram%20became%20very%20upset%20over%20this.%20He%20called%20his%20officers%20together%20and%20demanded%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWhich%20of%20you%20is%20the%20traitor%3F%20Who%20has%20been%20informing%20the%20king%20of%20Israel%20of%20my%20plans%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_12%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BIt%26%23x2019%3Bs%20not%20us%2C%20my%20lord%20the%20king%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20one%20of%20the%20officers%20replied.%20%26%23x201C%3BElisha%2C%20the%20prophet%20in%20Israel%2C%20tells%20the%20king%20of%20Israel%20even%20the%20words%20you%20speak%20in%20the%20privacy%20of%20your%20bedroom!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_13%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGo%20and%20find%20out%20where%20he%20is%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20king%20commanded%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Bso%20I%20can%20send%20troops%20to%20seize%20him.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EAnd%20the%20report%20came%20back%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BElisha%20is%20at%20Dothan.%26%23x201D%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_14%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20one%20night%20the%20king%20of%20Aram%20sent%20a%20great%20army%20with%20many%20chariots%20and%20horses%20to%20surround%20the%20city.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_15%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20the%20servant%20of%20the%20man%20of%20God%20got%20up%20early%20the%20next%20morning%20and%20went%20outside%2C%20there%20were%20troops%2C%20horses%2C%20and%20chariots%20everywhere.%20%26%23x201C%3BOh%2C%20sir%2C%20what%20will%20we%20do%20now%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20young%20man%20cried%20to%20Elisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_16%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BDon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20be%20afraid!%26%23x201D%3B%20Elisha%20told%20him.%20%26%23x201C%3BFor%20there%20are%20more%20on%20our%20side%20than%20on%20theirs!%26%23x201D%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_17%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Elisha%20prayed%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20open%20his%20eyes%20and%20let%20him%20see!%26%23x201D%3B%20The%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20opened%20the%20young%20man%26%23x2019%3Bs%20eyes%2C%20and%20when%20he%20looked%20up%2C%20he%20saw%20that%20the%20hillside%20around%20Elisha%20was%20filled%20with%20horses%20and%20chariots%20of%20fire.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_6_18%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EAs%20the%20Ara